		    <td width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
			I saw this named HG in Rathe while I was charming normal HGs. I made the mistake of having my 'pet' attack this guy and poor 'pet' died while Broog lost only about an eighth of his life. I dont have any more info other than he hits way harder than a normal HG. I am guessing level 40 as he brushed off my attempt to Charm him as a 30th level Bard.<BR>
Please give some more info/correct my info on this mob.
		  
