			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I just ran into this guy for the first time, I was soloing HG for loot on top of the mountain and I saw him spawn in.  I was at half mana, but he conned blue, so I figured at least I would get exp for the kill.  I sent my pet in and saw Broog hitting for not just 113, but 121! and I saw double hits.  I nuked him 3 times for 810, and got worried when it barely effected his life bar.  I sat down while my earth pet was tanking, I figured the only way to solo him on low mana was to chain cast pets.<BR>
<BR>
But as luck would have it, another HG behind me saw me sit down and jumped me.  before I had a chance to turn and run, he already had me at half life.  I started to run just as Broog tore through my earth pet, and now I couldnt cast another because I had a secont HG on me, so I ran for the hills, but not fast enough.  Broog double hit me in the back 2 more times for 121 and killed me.<BR>
<BR>
I am a lvl 52 mage, I'm sure I could kill him if FM and not jumped by others, but he is quite a foe.  I would have to confirm the estimate of about 8000-9000 HP, but my spells got through easily.  <BR>
<BR>
He despawned after killing me, so I cant tell you what the loot was.  But now I have a vendetta to repay...<BR>
<BR>
Eandori Raintree<BR>
High Elf Magician of the 52nd Circle<BR>
server- Solusek Ro<BR>
